claim: The Central American Integration System can observe sessions of the NATO Parliamentary Assembly.
premise_source_doc_sentence: She has participated in many world conferences , including the Fourth World Women 's Conference in Peking 1995 ; the World Food Summit in Rome 1996 ; the World Habitat Conference in Istanbul 1996 ; the First World Conference on Globalization in Santiago de Compostella , in Spain , 1997 ; sessions of the Parliamentary Assembly of the Council of Europe 1996 , 1997 and 1998 ; the NATO Parliamentary Assembly 1998 ; OSCE Ambassadors meeting in Vienna 1998 ; the Lansdowne Conference 1999 ; the Airlie Conference 2000 and 2002 ; and the International Conference on the Transfer of Peoples , Tallinn , Estonia , January 1992 .
